name: Material Library v1.2.3
body:
- Fix bugs.
- Widgets now extend from AppCompat views instead of Android views.
- Add `rd_delayRipple` and `sl_thumbTouchRadius` attributes..

name: Material Library v1.2.2
body:
- Fix some NPE bugs.
- Fix compatible bug with support library v23.1.1.

name: Material Library v1.2.0
body:
- Fix bugs.
- Add ThemeManager class and theme supporting for all widgets.
- Add `tv_fontFamily` attribute.
- Add `sl_alwaysFillThumb` attribute for Slider class.
- Add BottomSheetDialog class.

name: Material Library v1.1.1
body:
- Fix bugs.
- Add support RTL to widgets.
- Add `tp_leadingZero` attribute for `TimePickerDialog` class. 
- Change `rd_delayClick` to integer attribute.
- Add `lmd_layoutDirection` attribute to `LineMorphingDrawable` class.
- Add `onBuildDone(Dialog)` method to `Dialog.Buidler` class.
- Add `getSelectedItem()`, `setValueRange()` methods to `Slider` class.

name: Material Library v1.1.0
body:
- Fix bugs.
- Add default style.
- Change `ripple` attribute to `rd_style`, `delayClick` attribute to `rd_delayClick`. Add `rd_enable` attribute.
- Add `sb_text`, `sb_actionText`, `sb_duration` attributes for SnackBar class.
- Add `di_inAnimation`, `di_outAnimation` attributes for Dialog class.
- Add listener interface for Switch and Slider class.
